---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';

const article = { author: "Maine Dispensary Guide Editorial Team", publishDate: "2026-01-15", modifiedDate: "2026-03-28", section: "City Guides" };
---

<Layout 
  title="Auburn Dispensary Guide | Maine Dispensary Guide" 
  description="Auburn, Maine cannabis dispensary guide. 2026 market opportunities, strategic locations, local fee structures, and OCP investment requirements."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500916434205-0c77489c6cf7?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
  article={article}
>
  <article>
    <div class="article-header">
      <h1>Auburn Dispensary Guide</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">How to open a cannabis dispensary in Auburn, Maine</p>
    </div>

    <section class="fact-box">
      <h2>📋 Auburn at a Glance</h2>
      <table>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>License Required</strong></td><td>Maine OCP Adult-Use Retail License</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Local Fee</strong></td><td>$2,500 annually</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>School Buffer</strong></td><td>500 ft minimum</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Commercial Rent</strong></td><td>$12-18/sq ft annually</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Current Dispensaries</strong></td><td>3-4 (opportunity)</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Why Auburn?</h2>
      <p>Auburn pairs with Lewiston to form Maine's second-largest metro area. Auburn offers slightly lower costs than Lewiston with access to the same 60,000+ regional customer base.</p>
    </section>

    <Callout title="Twin City Advantage" type="passion">
      Auburn and Lewiston work together as one economic region. By positioning in Auburn, you get access to the entire Lewiston-Auburn market while often paying lower rent than downtown Lewiston.
    </Callout>

    <section>
      <h2>Market Data</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Factor</th><th>Assessment</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Population</td><td>24,000+</td></tr>
          <tr><td>L-A Metro</td><td>60,000+</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Competition</td><td>Low-Moderate</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Access</td><td>I-95, Route 136</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Local X-Factor: The Retail Corridor</h2>
      <p><strong>What sets Auburn apart:</strong> Auburn is home to the Auburn Mall and several big-box retail centers. These generate consistent traffic that can benefit nearby dispensaries.</p>
      <p><strong>Strategic Implication:</strong> Location near the mall or Target area provides built-in customer traffic without relying on downtown foot traffic.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Best Locations</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Area</th><th>Pros</th><th>Rent/Sq Ft</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>Center Street</strong></td><td>Downtown Auburn</td><td>$14-18</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Mount Auburn Area</strong></td><td>Near Auburn Mall</td><td>$12-16</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Washington Street</strong></td><td>Highway access</td><td>$14-17</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Takeaways</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>✅ Opportunity:</strong> L-A market with lower costs</li>
        <li><strong>✅ Advantage:</strong> Mall retail traffic</li>
        <li><strong>💰 Investment:</strong> $300K-400K</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="further-reading">
      <h2>Resources</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine OCP</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-license/">License Guide</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>Informational only.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2, section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; }
  section h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .further-reading { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .further-reading h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .fact-box { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.1); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary); }
  .fact-box h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .fact-box table { margin: 0; }
</style>